# Split conjunctive filter

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `predicate_pushdown_rules()` to a declarative
`.rra` rule (RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (filter (and ?p1 ?p2) ?input)
rhs: (filter ?p1 (filter ?p2 ?input))
